Market Analysis and Insights :

Global Superdisintegrants Market

The superdisintegrants market is expected to witness market growth at a rate of 7.50% in the forecast period of 2022 to 2029. Data Bridge Market Research report on superdisintegrants market provides analysis and insights regarding the various factors expected to be prevalent throughout the forecast period while providing their impacts on the market’s growth. The rise in healthcare sector globally is escalating the growth of superdisintegrants market.

Superdisintegrants refer to the modified disintegrants that are added in drug formulations for facilitating the breakup or disintegration of tablets or capsules into smaller particles. They help in enhancing the absorption of the drug and the solubility of active pharmaceutical ingredients (APIs) in the body. They reduce the disintegration time or oral solid dosage forms. These are used at a low level in the solid dosage form, generally 1- 10% by weight relative to the total weight of the dosage unit.

The increase in the adoption of orally disintegrating tablets across the globe acts as one of the major factors driving the growth of superdisintegrants market. The rise in number of people suffering from various age-related and chronic diseases among population, and increase in demand of the product owning to the high compatibility, improved bioavailability, and efficient compressibility accelerate the market growth. The use of superdisintegrants in the production of orally disintegrating tablets (ODTs) for antipsychotics, antidepressants, antimigraine, and sedatives, and surge in pediatric patients and the geriatric population further influence the market. Additionally, rise in healthcare expenditure, growth in awareness, increase in the prevalence of unhealthy lifestyle and development in technology positively affect the superdisintegrants market. Furthermore, development and innovation of novel formulations extend profitable opportunities to the market players in the forecast period of 2022 to 2029.

On the other hand, high cost associated with the treatment and diagnosis is expected to obstruct the market growth. Low awareness among people is projected to challenge the superdisintegrants market in the forecast period of 2022-2029.

